data.text: As you may know, this honor is reserved for students at the top of their class with G.P.A.â€™s of 3.6 and above. Through your dedicated pursuit of academic excellence you are maximizing the benefits of your college experience, and opening doors for the future! Your hard work and engagement enriches the Drew community in innumerable ways. Again, congratulations on your outstanding academic performance!
